  "text": "We rely on standard methods for creating and querying the inverted index [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] . Creating the index in our implementation for one million images takes roughly 4 hours, a query for 50 images takes a couple of seconds, depending on the number of distinct visual words in the query. Note that those timings could be easily improved, this, however, was not the focus of this work.",
